            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je m’écoute, avec des frissons ardents,\nMoi, le petit faune au regard farouche…\nL’âme des forêts vit entre mes dents\nEt le dieu du rythme habite ma bouche."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Dans ce bois, loin des ægipans rôdeurs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5−5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Mon cœur est plus doux qu’une rose ouverte ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Les rayons, chargés d’heureuses odeurs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Dansent au son frais de la flûte verte.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dans ce bois, loin des ægipans rôdeurs,\nMon cœur est plus doux qu’une rose ouverte ;\nLes rayons, chargés d’heureuses odeurs,\nDansent au son frais de la flûte verte."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Mêlez vos cheveux et joignez vos bras",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Tandis qu’à vos pieds le bélier s’ébroue,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Nymphes des halliers ! — ne m’approchez pas !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Allez rire ailleurs pendant que je joue.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mêlez vos cheveux et joignez vos bras\nTandis qu’à vos pieds le bélier s’ébroue,\nNymphes des halliers ! — ne m’approchez pas !\nAllez rire ailleurs pendant que je joue."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Car j’ai la pudeur de mon art sacré,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Et pour honorer la Muse hautaine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Je chercherai l’ombre et je cacherai",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Mes pipeaux vibrants dans le creux d’un chêne…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Car j’ai la pudeur de mon art sacré,\nEt pour honorer la Muse hautaine,\nJe chercherai l’ombre et je cacherai\nMes pipeaux vibrants dans le creux d’un chêne…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Parmi la tiédeur, parmi les parfums,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Je jouerai le long du jour, jusqu’à l’heure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Des chœurs turbulents et des jeux communs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Et des seins offerts que la brise effleure…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Parmi la tiédeur, parmi les parfums,\nJe jouerai le long du jour, jusqu’à l’heure\nDes chœurs turbulents et des jeux communs\nEt des seins offerts que la brise effleure…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Je tairai mon chant pieux et loyal",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Aux amants de vin, aux chercheurs de proie…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Seul le vent du soir apprendra mon mal",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Et les arbres seuls connaîtront ma joie.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je tairai mon chant pieux et loyal\nAux amants de vin, aux chercheurs de proie…\nSeul le vent du soir apprendra mon mal\nEt les arbres seuls connaîtront ma joie."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Je défends ainsi mes instants meilleurs…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Vous qui m’épiez de vos yeux de chèvres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Ô mes compagnons ! allez rire ailleurs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Pendant que le chant fleurit sur mes lèvres.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je défends ainsi mes instants meilleurs…\nVous qui m’épiez de vos yeux de chèvres,\nÔ mes compagnons ! allez rire ailleurs\nPendant que le chant fleurit sur mes lèvres."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Sinon, — je suis faune après tout, si beau",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Que soit mon hymne, — et, bouc qui se rebiffe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Je me vengerai d’un coup de sabot",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Et d’un coup de corne et d’un coup de griffe.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sinon, — je suis faune après tout, si beau\nQue soit mon hymne, — et, bouc qui se rebiffe,\nJe me vengerai d’un coup de sabot\nEt d’un coup de corne et d’un coup de griffe."
        }
